  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Go on a summer vacation to the Cloudy Valley archipelago!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take your time to explore the archipelago, dive into the blue sea among the fish, find treasures, and climb to the heights to appreciate the landscapes.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600720/extras/8de009bcc195ec281a737355b5170d95.poster.avif?t=1770722427\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600720/extras/8de009bcc195ec281a737355b5170d95.webm?t=1770722427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the archipelago without constraints: run, climb, swim to discover new islands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the inhabitants of Cloudy Valley and the life of the archipelago, pet the wild sheep and farm moles, and take part in token hunting contests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the first to catch a rainbow trout, or catch some fish for the archipelago's inhabitants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate in keeping the archipelago clean by picking up the garbage you find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect a variety of hats and choose the one that suits you best!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go at your own pace and enjoy a cozy summer atmosphere. Expect a 2 to 4 hours adventure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax in a peaceful atmosphere by listening to the gentle melodies composed by Gregor Hadjiganev, whether by the water, in a forest, or atop a cliff...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600720/extras/10b1d8ba164027381e7bd06541f4dc97.poster.avif?t=1770722427\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600720/extras/10b1d8ba164027381e7bd06541f4dc97.webm?t=1770722427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Prepare your bag for a peaceful adventure in Cloudy Valley. Rest for a few hours in a calm and soothing atmosphere...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600720/extras/d242d446ec3acdc9c7d3514c87fa6f73.avif?t=1770722427\" width=616 height=432 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Go on a summer vacation to the Cloudy Valley archipelago!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take your time to explore the archipelago, dive into the blue sea among the fish, find treasures, and climb to the heights to appreciate the landscapes.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600720/extras/8de009bcc195ec281a737355b5170d95.poster.avif?t=1770722427\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600720/extras/8de009bcc195ec281a737355b5170d95.webm?t=1770722427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the archipelago without constraints: run, climb, swim to discover new islands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the inhabitants of Cloudy Valley and the life of the archipelago, pet the wild sheep and farm moles, and take part in token hunting contests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the first to catch a rainbow trout, or catch some fish for the archipelago's inhabitants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate in keeping the archipelago clean by picking up the garbage you find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect a variety of hats and choose the one that suits you best!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go at your own pace and enjoy a cozy summer atmosphere. Expect a 2 to 4 hours adventure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax in a peaceful atmosphere by listening to the gentle melodies composed by Gregor Hadjiganev, whether by the water, in a forest, or atop a cliff...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600720/extras/10b1d8ba164027381e7bd06541f4dc97.poster.avif?t=1770722427\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600720/extras/10b1d8ba164027381e7bd06541f4dc97.webm?t=1770722427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Prepare your bag for a peaceful adventure in Cloudy Valley. Rest for a few hours in a calm and soothing atmosphere...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600720/extras/d242d446ec3acdc9c7d3514c87fa6f73.avif?t=1770722427\" width=616 height=432 /></span></p>",
